    {
      "id": "PopularPost9326",
      "post_content": "This card is very useful early, mid, and late game. Turn 3 onto a Naya Hushblade is amazing. +1/+1 and shroud for multicolor, +2/+2 for enchantment, then firebreathing and lifelink. It's a good way to start off a match.   \nAlso, I have topdecked this card many times late game to pull off the win. They don't stack as well as Edge of the Divinity's do, since additional firebreathing is useless, and once the new rules kick in, the additional lifelink won't matter either.  \nVery good card.",
      "posted_by": "Kenji18",
